Activity 1: Creation of Picklist field for Contact object:

1. Go to Setup → Click on Object Manager
2. Type object name Contact in the Quick Find box → Click on Contact 
3. Click on Fields & Relationships 
4. Click on New 
5. Select Data Type as Picklist and click Next 
6. Enter the Field Label as Education Level 
7. Click on Enter values and enter: a. Graduation b. UG c. Diploma 
8. Click Next, Next, and Save

Activity 2: Creation of Lookup field for Opportunity Object:

Go to the Setup page >> click on Object manager >> type object name (Opportunity) in the quick find bar >> click on the Opportunity object.
Click on Fields & Relationship
Click on New.
Select “Lookup relationship” as data type and click Next.
Select the related object “User”.
Click on Next.
Give Field Label as “Counselor Assigned”.
Click on Next, Next, Next, Save.
